menu.description: Cheese Quesadilla, Nachitos, Chimichangitas, Sour Cream and Guacamole. A perfect sampler for sharing (or not!), our Combo Appetizer includes a crispy cheese quesadilla, golden nachitos topped with melted cheese, and mini chimichangitas filled with savory goodness. Served with cool sour cream and fresh guacamole on the side, this platter brings together bold flavors and crunchy textures for the ultimate start to any meal.

A hearty twist on a classic favoritecrispy tortilla chips layered with refried beans and melted cheese, then topped with fresh jalapeos, diced onions, ripe tomatoes, and creamy avocado. Bold, satisfying, and perfect for sharing.

A fiesta on a platter! Our Nachos Grande starts with a bed of crisp tortilla chips layered with refried beans and melted cheese, then loaded with your choice of savory ground beef, shredded chicken, picadillo, carne asada, carnitas al pastor, or melted cheese. Topped with diced onions, tomatoes, jalapeos, creamy guacamole, and cool sour cream, its a bold, shareable appetizeror a full meal on its own

Golden French fries piled high and smothered with tender grilled carne asada, melted cheese, fresh diced tomatoes, chopped onions, and spicy jalapeos. Topped with creamy guacamole and a dollop of sour cream for the perfect balance of flavor and heat. A bold and satisfying favorite you wont want to share!

White Shrimp, Lemon Juice, Cucumber, Pico de Gallo, Avocado. Refreshing and zesty, our shrimp ceviche features tender white shrimp marinated in freshly squeezed lemon juice, mixed with crisp cucumber, vibrant pico de gallo, and creamy avocado. A bright and satisfying seafood dish bursting with bold, citrusy flavorperfect as a starter or a light entre.

Crispy, golden corn tortillas rolled and filled with your choice of tender shredded chicken or seasoned picadillo. Served with fresh cheese, creamy guacamole, sour cream, and crisp shredded lettuce for a crunchy, flavorful bite in every piece. A classic favorite, made mini and perfect for sharingor not!

Avocado, Onion and Lime. Guacamole A simple, fresh blend of creamy avocado, finely chopped onion, and a splash of zesty lime juice. Smooth, vibrant, and made to orderperfect as a dip, side, or topping.

Giant Flour Tortilla and Monterey Jack Cheese Cheese Quesadilla A giant flour tortilla grilled to golden perfection and stuffed with melted Monterey Jack cheese. Crisp on the outside, gooey on the insidethis classic comfort dish is perfect on its own or as a cheesy side to any meal

A giant grilled flour tortilla loaded with melted Monterey Jack cheese and your choice of tender grilled chicken, juicy steak, or a mouthwatering combo. Stuffed with sauted bell peppers and onions, then served with creamy guacamole and cool sour cream on the side. A bold, cheesy twist on classic fajitascrispy, savory, and made to satisfy.

Miniature flour tortillas rolled and lightly fried to a golden crisp, filled with your choice of savory chicken, seasoned picadillo, or mixed vegetables. Served with cool sour cream and fresh guacamole on the side. Crunchy on the outside, warm and flavorful on the insideperfect as a snack or starter.
A fresh, crisp mix of greens topped with juicy tomato, sliced red onion, cool cucumber, and shredded carrot. Light, vibrant, and perfect as a starter or a refreshing side.

A crisp tortilla bowl filled with your choice of Ground Beef, Picadillo, Chicken, or Mixed Vegetables, layered with fresh lettuce, shredded cheese, creamy guacamole, house-made pico de gallo, and a dollop of sour cream. Bold, fresh, and satisfyingperfectly packed with flavor.

A crispy fried flour tortilla layered with refried beans, melted cheese, and your choice of Ground Beef, Picadillo, Chicken, or Mixed Vegetables. Topped with fresh lettuce, diced tomato, avocado slices, and a dollop of sour creamhearty, crunchy, and full of bold Mexican flavor.

A comforting cup of traditional Mexican tortilla soup, made with a rich tomato-chile broth and topped with crispy tortilla strips, avocado, melted cheese, and a touch of crema. Bold, warm flavors in a perfect starter size.

A hearty bowl of traditional Mexican tortilla soup featuring a robust tomato and chile-infused broth. Generously topped with crispy tortilla strips, fresh avocado, melted cheese, and a swirl of crema. Bold, satisfying, and full of comforting flavorperfect as a main course.
Juicy grilled chicken atop crisp mixed greens, fresh tomato slices, and creamy avocado. A simple yet flavorful Mexican-style salad thats light, refreshing, and satisfying.
